Package: IBAid
Title: Interval-based Allelic Imbalance Detection Method
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mona", "Arabzadeh", , "arabzadeh.mona@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Calculate AB ratio and confidence interval (CI) of allele counts A,B based on propagation of uncertainties for depth calculation; and decide on Imbalance/Balance phenotype of each gene in each sample.
